abstract.text: Perform arithmetic and logical functions on large integers.

inlineContent.text: The vBigNum module provides arithmetic and logical operations on large integers with lengths of 128, 256, 512, or 1024 bits.
vBigNum includes data types that represent large integer quantities, such as
, which defines a 512-bit signed integer. The function names begin with the data type, followed by the name of the operation. For example,
performs the addition of two 512-bit signed integers.

abstract.text: Make large-scale mathematical computations and image calculations, optimized for high performance and low energy consumption.
